Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friendship! Romance! Mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We try our best because we've made those promises!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An ordinary train station with an unusual case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mere piece of paper's distance separates good and evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:02:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you're always drinking juice that you have to go to the restroom so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was really good, wasn't it, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only Ran-neechan could've come...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be helped since she had some club activity suddenly come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get some good ramen before going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More food?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't enjoy the French cuisine because my back was sore from the seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let's take a detour!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next stop is Nishi-Sumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nishi-Sumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:42.70,Top,,0,0,0,,HIDDEN CIRCUMSTANCES OF THE FALLING INCIDENT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The train is now approaching the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll order the salty flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, are you really going, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, can't they just get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, stop the fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector Gotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Mouri-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Gotou from the Nishi-Sumida Police Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard about you a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never thought I'd run into you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just so happens that he witnessed the fight that led to this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I suppose that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's great then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be a pleasure to have Mouri-san working on this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, the pleasure's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just let me, Mouri Kogorou, take care of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we know the victim's identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furuta Keisuke-san, age 41.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He works at a nearby company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He usually takes this express train to work, and was likely on his way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is a fracture to his skull due to the impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who got into a fight with him was Sugimoto Hideki-san, age 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.96,Top,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto Hideki (27)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A company employee from the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Gotou from Nishi-Sumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a few questions to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too loud here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, please feel free to use our employee break room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moriya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on my way home today after treating a customer to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got up to use the restroom, and left my bag on the rack while I was in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stayed in there a while due to an upset stomach, and when I returned my bag was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when we reached the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw that guy leaving with my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.49,Top,,0,0,0,,Furuta Keisuke (42)\NCompany Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he refused to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's what you two fought over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when I tried to take my bag back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The strap broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And unfortunately, they hadn't yet put the safety fence around the construction site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you'd never met Furuta-san before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Mouri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's truly a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Furuta-san had never taken Sugimoto-san's bag in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of this would've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Furuta-san really take that bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he have mistaken it for lost luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lost luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's brought lost items to us before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rare to find kind people like him nowadays, and everyone here speaks highly of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't think he's the kind of person who would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If what you've said is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the victim may have already tried to determine the identity of the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, go confirm this with the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, please hold on, Sugimoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to wait for testimony from witnesses first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as the station worker said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Furuta-san attempted to find the bag's owner before getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are passengers who remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to them, Furuta-san had gotten on the train after Sugimoto-san went to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, Sugimoto-san left his bag on the rack and went to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, Furuta-san got on the train and took the bag thinking that someone had forgotten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Sugimoto-san didn't know this, and thought that his bag had been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then found Furuta-san among the other passengers with your bag, and tried to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From Furuta-san's point of view, after confirming that the owner was not around...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be feasible to believe that someone suddenly appeared to claim it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead, with his strong sense of righteousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got into a struggle while attempting to protect the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And ended up dying in an unfortunate accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about you, Sugimoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it really necessary to get in a fight over such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He intended to take it to the lost & found out of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But ended up dying in such a resentful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, you can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The receipt is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Receipt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The receipt from when I treated that customer to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was with the rest of the money in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now it's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure they aren't in your pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I clearly remember putting it in my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they fell on the station floor during the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saitou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that it did not fall out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've retrieved Furuta-san's belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A multi-course dinner in Sasayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, may I see that for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my missing receipt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, "Sugimoto Hideki-sama."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the amount charged is the same, 25,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why was it in Furuta-san's pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only happened once, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was an incident wherein money was missing from an item Furuta-san turned in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:11:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furuta-san was also suspected at that time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A thief usually wouldn't turn in the rest of the items.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furuta-san could have stolen the money while pretending to just turn the bag in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a common form of theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Form of theft?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he refused to return the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would expose his crime if he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to think it ended like that for Furuta-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case, please check to see if anything else is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, for the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind filling this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, can I borrow a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies, I forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's how it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The true secret behind this accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's so important that it can't wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd that brat Conan go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After calling me all the way over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, we're all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Gotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san wants all of us to come to the boarding area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boarding area?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Mouri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This pose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the renowned Sleeping Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mouri-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case was just an accident due to a luggage misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's incorrect, Inspector Gotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll explain it to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, let us first review Sugimoto-san's testimony again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, after Sugimoto-san returned from the restroom, he noticed his bag was missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he saw Furuta-san with it in the station, so he quickly left the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, when we saw it happen, Sugimoto-san jumped out from behind the vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you find it odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:16:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he be there if he had just come off of the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he came from the complete opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:10.76,Top,,0,0,0,,Construction Area\NConstruction Materials\NFuruta\N1st Car\NVending Machine\NSugi-moto\NPlatform
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any sense to appear from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would Sugimoto-san do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Furuta-san to steal the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, you just made that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto-san most likely figured that Furuta-san would steal the money while pretending to turn in the lost bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he purposely put his receipt in his wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the receipt is found on Furuta-san, it would expose his thievery and make taking the bag back easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop pushing your claims!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To allow Furuta-san to steal the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto-san purposely left the bag on the rack when he went to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there were other passengers there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would Furuta-san know it was a lost bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cell phone was in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cell phone he took out probably had an unanswered call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just before the train pulled into the station, Sugimoto-san called that cell phone with another one from the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no one ended up answering the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore it seemed to be a lost bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of Sleeping Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:18:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furuta-san went and hid behind the construction zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after watching him steal the money out of the bag from the vending machine, Sugimoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Confronted Furuta-san and pushed him into the construction zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was then knocked to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, he had laid the warning sign face down on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had also cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then all he had to do was take the bag from the fallen victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Furuta-san didn't want the bag to be taken, he'd reach for the straps, which had already been weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After losing his balance, Furuta-san would fall off the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I need to check the straps of your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a premeditated murder disguised as an accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all just conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy was hanging onto my bag with all of his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forcing him to fall while we were arguing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could easily manage it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By using the ballpoint pen in the pocket of your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ballpoint pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While fighting behind the construction area...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stabbed Furuta-san with that ballpoint pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, you pushed him backward as he was getting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still there, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The marks you made on Furuta-san's right hand with your ballpoint pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he took...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My girlfriend's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she was crossing the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was speeding and ran her over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had decided to get married soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there were no other witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They believed his testimony that she suddenly jumped into the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard escaped punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could he...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you wanted to kill Furuta-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And decided to set up this trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was I supposed to forgive that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, it's ready to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.22,0:23:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the ramen place was closed, you didn't have to buy cup ramen to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have another!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for Uncle, this kind of food suits him better than that French cuisine.
